---
description: Core rules for the Sortex prototype
alwaysApply: true
---

Before editing, read `PROJECT_CONTEXT.md`, `ARCHITECTURE.md`, and `AGENTS.md`.

Keep changes small and task-scoped. Do not alter hardware, control, or vision contracts without updating `ARCHITECTURE.md` and tests. Parameters must come from config. Valves must default to OFF. After changes, run focused tests and report changed files, tests, assumptions, and limitations.
